          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Quarterly: Domain Steward Asset Review"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Four times a year, the domain steward refreshes their asset register and re-evaluates all approved sources:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Pull the current asset register and compare against what is live in the vector stores."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "For each approved source: confirm the source document(s) still exist and are current."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "For each approved source: confirm the ACL mapping still reflects actual access policy (role membership may have changed)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Review the quarter's health reports for any patterns worth addressing."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Sign and date the register; submit to the AI Governance Lead."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
