      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Every six months, each active Claude use case must be formally re-approved by the domain steward and the DPO. This catches cases where the risk profile has changed since initial approval — new user populations, expanded data sources, or updated regulatory guidance."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
