            "text": "# semi-annual-use-case-reapproval.yaml\n\nuse_case_id: \"legal-assistant-v1\"\nlast_approved: \"2024-12-15\"\nreapproval_due: \"2025-06-15\"\n\nchanges_since_last_approval:\n  - \"EU AI Act Article 6 now applicable — high-risk classification review needed\"\n  - \"User base expanded to include external counsel (contractor role)\"\n\nrisk_delta:\n  - risk: \"External counsel accessing internal policy docs via Claude\"\n    assessment: \"Acceptable with ACL restriction to approved external-counsel role\"\n    mitigation: \"Added 'external-counsel' role to ACL with restricted document set\"\n\ndecision: \"re-approved\"\ndomain_steward: \"Maria Chen\"\ndpo_sign_off: \"DPO Office\"\nreapproval_date: \"2025-06-10\"\nnext_review_due: \"2025-12-10\"\n"
